      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>New day</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>No matter how you look, </l>
          <l>You can only see a part of everything. </l>
          <l>No matter how you listen, </l>
          <l>You can only hear some of the sounds. </l>
          <l>The moment you quiet your mind, and you’re out of the way, </l>
          <l>You’ll know in your soul what a gift it is… </l>
          <l>Just to be around. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Don’t look for yourself outside, </l>
          <l>Be courageous - go shake hands with fear, </l>
          <l>Go within. </l>
          <l>When you’re on the other side, </l>
          <l>A ne day will begin. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>When you touch someone soul </l>
          <l>They will drink it in like water. </l>
          <l>When you look into their eyes </l>
          <l>You’ll be invited right in. </l>
          <l>When the smile on your face will turn a little bit softer, </l>
          <l>Harmony will begin.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
